1. Add these Thymeleaf dependencies :
    <dependency>
    	<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    	<artifactId>spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf</artifactId>
    </dependency>
    <dependency>
    	<groupId>org.thymeleaf</groupId>
    	<artifactId>thymeleaf-spring5</artifactId>
    	<version>3.1.2.RELEASE</version>
    </dependency>

2. under templates folder (src/resources/templates)
    - create verify-email.html file
    - create one more file i.e. password-reset-email.html